From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


Indian actress
Musskan SethiBornDelhiNationalityIndianOccupationActressYears active2017–present
Musskan Sethi is an Indian actress.[1][2][3] She is best known for her movies like Paisa Vasool and Raagala 24 Gantallo.[4][5][6]


Early life and career[edit]
Sethi was born in Delhi.[7] In 2017, She made her debut with the film Paisa Vasool.[8] In 2019, she acted in the film Raagala 24 Gantallo and High-End Yaariyan.[7]

Filmography[edit]
Paisa Vasool  (2017) as Harika
Raagala 24 Gantallo (2019) as Meghna
High End Yaariyan as Mandy
Sayonee (2020)
Radha krishna[9]
Maro Prasthanam[10]
